description: Tourn International AB engages in the development and operation of digital platforms. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2013-12-18. The platform Tourn.se offers the advertising network, which connects advertisers with influencers, so that businesses can market their products in social media, such as Instagram, Twitter, YouTube, Facebook and others. Also, the Company develops technical platforms to ensure the transparency of buyers, analysis and measurable results for accuracy to each audience through display and content marketing. Additionally, Tourn International AB (publ) runs adProton, the advertising network focusing on applications that deliver advertising solutions and publishing opportunities for application developers.
name: Tourn International AB (publ)
